Source: openresty-stap2
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: OpenResty Admin <admin@openresty.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), g++, gettext, m4, zlib1g-dev, liblzma-dev,
 libbz2-dev, openresty-elfutils-dev (>= 0.177.12), openresty-perl, openresty-perl-cpanel-json-xs
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Homepage: http://sourceware.org/systemtap/

Package: openresty-stap2-sdt-dev
Architecture: any
Section: devel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Static probe support tools (OpenResty's fork of SystemTap)
 OpenResty's fork of SystemTap sdt-devel includes the <sys/sdt.h> header file
 used for static instrumentation compiled into userspace programs and libraries,
 along with the optional dtrace-compatibility preprocessor to process related
 .d files into tracing-macro-laden .h headers.

Package: openresty-stap2-runtime
Architecture: any
Section: devel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Programmable system-wide instrumentation system - runtime (OpenResty's fork of SystemTap)
 OpenResty's fork of SystemTap runtime contains the components needed to execute
 a systemtap script that was already compiled into a module
 using a local or remote systemtap-devel installation.

Package: openresty-stap2
Architecture: any
Section: devel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libbz2-dev, liblzma5, zlib1g, make,
 openresty-stap2-runtime (>= 4.2.0.2), openresty-elfutils (>= 0.177.12),
 openresty-perl, openresty-perl-cpanel-json-xs
Description: OpenResty's fork of SystemTap
 OpenResty's fork of SystemTap is an instrumentation system for systems running Linux.
 Developers can write instrumentation scripts to collect data on
 the operation of the system. The base systemtap package contains/requires
 the components needed to locally develop and execute systemtap scripts.
 Requires(pre): shadow-utils

Package: openresty-stap2-dbgsym
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, openresty-stap2 (>= 4.2.0.2)
Description: Debug symbols for the openresty-stap2 package
 Debug symbols (or debuginfo) for the openresty-stap2 package.

Package: openresty-stap2-tests
Architecture: all
Section: devel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Test suite for the openresty-stap2 package.
